preference.name: ADA_saveas_propagated_license_types
preference.preference_description: Specifies the list of license types that are copied over to the new object during the "Save As", "Revise" and "Baseline" operations. If the preference "TC_copy_security_data_exclusion_list" contains the property "license_list", no license type is copied.
